@ReadingTracker.Api_HostAddress = https://localhost:7000

### Health Check
GET {{ReadingTracker.Api_HostAddress}}/health

### Get all user books
GET {{ReadingTracker.Api_HostAddress}}/api/userbooks

### Search books externally
GET {{ReadingTracker.Api_HostAddress}}/api/booksearch/search?query=the hobbit&maxResults=5

### Search book by ISBN
GET {{ReadingTracker.Api_HostAddress}}/api/booksearch/isbn/9780544003415

### Add book to library
POST {{ReadingTracker.Api_HostAddress}}/api/userbooks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookId": "978-0544003415",
  "bookInfo": {
    "title": "The Hobbit",
    "author": "J.R.R. Tolkien",
    "isbn": "978-0544003415",
    "publisher": "Houghton Mifflin Harcourt",
    "publicationYear": 1937,
    "totalPages": 310,
    "genre": "Fantasy",
    "description": "A reluctant hobbit, Bilbo Baggins, sets out to the Lonely Mountain with a spirited group of dwarves to reclaim their mountain home and the gold within it from the dragon Smaug.",
    "coverImageUrl": "https://example.com/hobbit-cover.jpg"
  },
  "personalNotes": "Classic fantasy adventure"
}

### Update book status to reading
PUT {{ReadingTracker.Api_HostAddress}}/api/userbooks/12345678-1234-1234-1234-123456789012/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "reading",
  "date": "2024-01-15T10:00:00Z"
}

### Log reading session
POST {{ReadingTracker.Api_HostAddress}}/api/userbooks/12345678-1234-1234-1234-123456789012/sessions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionDate": "2024-01-15T19:00:00Z",
  "startPage": 1,
  "endPage": 25,
  "endTime": "2024-01-15T20:30:00Z",
  "sessionNotes": "Great opening chapter, loved the description of the Shire"
}

### Update reading progress
PUT {{ReadingTracker.Api_HostAddress}}/api/userbooks/12345678-1234-1234-1234-123456789012/progress
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pageNumber": 150
}

### Rate book
PUT {{ReadingTracker.Api_HostAddress}}/api/userbooks/12345678-1234-1234-1234-123456789012/rating
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rating": 5
}

### Update personal notes
PUT {{ReadingTracker.Api_HostAddress}}/api/userbooks/12345678-1234-1234-1234-123456789012/notes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "personalNotes": "One of the best fantasy books I've ever read. Tolkien's world-building is incredible."
}

### Mark book as finished
PUT {{ReadingTracker.Api_HostAddress}}/api/userbooks/12345678-1234-1234-1234-123456789012/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "finished",
  "date": "2024-01-20T22:00:00Z"
}

### Get reading statistics
GET {{ReadingTracker.Api_HostAddress}}/api/statistics

### Get books by status
GET {{ReadingTracker.Api_HostAddress}}/api/statistics/by-status/reading

### Get recently finished books
GET {{ReadingTracker.Api_HostAddress}}/api/statistics/recently-finished?days=30

### Get books by rating
GET {{ReadingTracker.Api_HostAddress}}/api/statistics/by-rating/5

### Get books by author
GET {{ReadingTracker.Api_HostAddress}}/api/statistics/by-author?author=tolkien

### Search user books
GET {{ReadingTracker.Api_HostAddress}}/api/userbooks/search?query=fantasy

### Get statistics counts
GET {{ReadingTracker.Api_HostAddress}}/api/statistics/counts

### Get currently reading books
GET {{ReadingTracker.Api_HostAddress}}/api/userbooks/by-status/reading

